Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:05.57,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama Shigeo, also known as Mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:07.39,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A second-year in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:13.74,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The second year of middle school kicks off\Nthe most sensitive period in one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.28,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,People call it adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.87,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Some hone their bodies playing sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:22.12,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,some work hard on their studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.58,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,some devote themselves to their hobbies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:26.92,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,some polish their talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.17,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,some rebel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:32.30,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and some fall for the opposite sex
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.47,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and get a taste of bittersweet love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:40.93,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,All those youthful desires come together to\Nform the amalgamation that is adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:44.57,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And Mob was spending that \Nprecious time working as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:48.32,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,an assistant at a psychic business \Nfor 300 yen an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.14,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is porn sites!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.53,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.07,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Porn sites...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.34,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The curse that is on your shoulder is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.08,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,a terrible one-click curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.51,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HDDF46B&}Doubts About Youth\N~The Telepathy Club Appears~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.88,sign_4283_38_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits and Such\NConsultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.88,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-A one-click curse from porn sites?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.26,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,They use illegal 18+ sites \Nto curse your shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.64,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,and make you pay fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.73,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Curses nowadays are becoming digital, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.27,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell would believe that hogwash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.90,Main,Reii,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't move for a second. \NI'll lift the curse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.86,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.49,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Your right shoulder is stiff—\NThe curse is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.04,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm not paying for this. Sto—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.67,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? It actually feels good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorcery Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.67,sign_2575_34_Sorcery_Crush,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sorcery\NCrush
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.21,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.67,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Reigen's special move
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.76,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,where he relieves the stress \Nfrom physical fatigue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.18,sign_2678_39_Abeshi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1016)}Abeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.55,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and gets ride of stiff \Nshoulders and back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.44,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that I was able to \Nlift the curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.94,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,but do your shoulders still feel heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.73,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I doubted you. \NI feel much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.44,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,May I come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.78,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.45,sign_3183_45_Reception,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.45,sign_3183_46_Manual,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.45,sign_3183_47_If_there_are_3_e,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,If there are 3 evil spirits,\Nthe exorcism fee on 1 of \Nthem will be on the house!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.45,sign_3183_48_Until_Month_s_En,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,This Month Only
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:45.45,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,So the 40-minute massage course \Nfee comes to 3,800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.24,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't call it the massage fee! \NCall it the curse-dispelling fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.58,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Your change is 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.08,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You'll eat some won't you, Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.92,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure. I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.34,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Master Reigen, you're getting \Nmuch better at massages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.88,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. I've been trying\N various methods to improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.80,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,like reading books on Seitai and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.56,sign_3783_57_Limited_Time_Cam,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Limited-Time Offer\N{\c&H474949&}If there are 3 evil spirits,\Nthe exorcism fee on 1 of\Nthem will be on the house!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.56,sign_3783_58_Until_Month_s_En,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,This Month Only
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.31,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's only effective \Nbecause of spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:11.98,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:13.89,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Such a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.69,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.90,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.28,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You never try to start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.99,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can use a little ESP and \NI'm different from other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:32.00,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to discuss that with you \Nand ended up becoming your student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.88,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I didn't have anyone \Nelse to talk to, so I'm grateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.38,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,because you teach me various \Nthings and pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.09,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,However, is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.47,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been thinking lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:54.56,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Does he think his pay is too little? \NOr did he finally find me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.64,sign_4888_72_Fake,One,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,561)}Fake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.64,sign_4902_73_Liar,Two,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,561)}Liar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.64,sign_4908_74_Con_Artist,Three,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,561)}Con Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.64,sign_4914_75_Self_Proclaimed_,Four,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,561)}Self-Proclaimed Psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.69,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.90,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.53,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than things ending with me \Nworking part-time after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.69,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that there may or may not be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.16,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,some other things that I \Ncan only experience now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.16,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.87,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.83,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Such is puberty, Mob-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.83,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something that \Nyou want to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.96,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Be in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.21,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.84,sign_5509_88_To_Wakkanai,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(528,518)}To Wakkanai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.63,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hitchhike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.05,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't have anything particular in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.47,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:27.93,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.80,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,In my expert opinion, I'd say the \Ngoing-home club is the absolute best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.52,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You're just goofing off during \Nthe period you can goof off the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.31,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,and that makes you a winner in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:40.48,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on lazing around and \Nmake money from me. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.07,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.11,Main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,I get treated like a weirdo \Njust for being in this club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:48.07,sign_6139_97_Telepathy_Club,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Telepathy Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.07,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.32,Main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.04,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.75,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,A club must have five\N or more members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.04,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.13,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.80,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find new members \Nlike our lives depend on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.21,sign_6604_106_Telepathy_Club_P,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)}Telepathy Club President:\NKurata Tome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.47,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Takenaka-san came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.47,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it! Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.89,sign_6796_109_Student_Council,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Student\NCouncil
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.73,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,I just received a submission of resignation \Nfrom this club, so be forewarned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.85,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.23,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,The student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.52,sign_6982_113_Student_Council_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council Vice President:\NTokugawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.52,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,This club will now be abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.98,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,Abolished?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.73,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.07,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, I'm going to have to ask you\Nto gather all of your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.45,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,I actually just had a brand-new club\N request a club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.03,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Quit jumping the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.45,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let you \Nabolish the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.79,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,The Telepathy Club bond is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.87,Main,Kij,0000,0000,0000,,The student council's got nothing on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.84,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're all high-and-mighty \Nbecause of how you part your hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.30,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Do you really want me to get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.09,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that desperate \Nto keep this club going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.18,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,bring me a new club member by\Nthe end of the school day on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.35,sign_6139_97_Telepathy_Club,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Telepathy Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.35,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,B-By Friday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.60,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,That only gives us two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.15,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.77,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Quit whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.86,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,If we ask everyone we see to join, \Nwe'll be able to snag at least one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.74,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible. \NRecruiting season ended a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.83,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm going to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:19.25,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We have overcome so many obstacles \Nup until now, haven't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.75,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.92,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done a single thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.01,sign_8577_138_The_Next_Day_Aft,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Next Day After School
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.68,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Telepathy Club? Sorry, what the hell\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.18,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.43,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.72,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Abolished? What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.10,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You should be studying. \NWe've got entrance exams this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.02,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are there hot guys? \NDo you have any hot guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.15,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.90,sign_9042_146_Girls_Bathroom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Girls Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.90,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be worried about the stares, \Nand it seems dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.32,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.07,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.40,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.32,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:55.74,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.16,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:56.83,Main,Person,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.08,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.96,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,It really was impossible to find \Nnew members this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.46,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention we just keep \Ngetting called creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.46,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Now even I want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.88,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.72,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,The president's lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.06,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.64,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,The going-home club...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:23.85,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.40,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought him! He's not \Nin any clubs or committees,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.02,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,and he doesn't seem to have a \Ngirlfriend or any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.86,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Salt Middle School's final\Ngo-homer and all-round bum,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.99,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama Shigeo-kun of class 2-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.61,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's basically right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.87,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Inukawa! Let me introduce you \Nto the other members, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.04,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kijibayashi, and Saruta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:40.87,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.66,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.96,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the president, \NKurata Tome, from class 3-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.88,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Tome-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.84,Italics,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,The president is desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:57.14,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Tome-chan... That's my grandmother's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.56,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure that's because of fate, too! \NThere you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.81,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Join the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.85,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.23,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.36,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Mob! You actually have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:12.03,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After this, I have \Nto go to my exorcism job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.57,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,E-Exorcism? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:18.99,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, President! Actually, this guy \Nwas sort of famous in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.12,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,He could bend spoons and make erasers move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.08,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.33,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,He's an esper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.46,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being weird and just join our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.09,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the exorcism can \Nwait a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.67,sign_4283_38_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits and Such \NConsultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.84,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up, Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.97,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.89,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I'm a little late today? \NI'm being recruited into a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.93,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That should be over instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.56,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No, I actually have to wait until \Nthe student council meeting is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.90,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,and then go submit my club admission form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:53.19,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait. So if I tell you I need you to \Ncome immediately, you're not going to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:57.36,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well... Shouldn't I keep \Nthe promise I made first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.62,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not like you actually want to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.82,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.70,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.29,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Show them how fast someone in the \Ngoing-home club can leave school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.67,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He says he needs me right away,\Nso I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.96,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,P-Put me on for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.80,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,I really need Kageyama-kun to \Njoin this club, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.59,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, eh? She must be trying to use Mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.89,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Mob's not the type to play any sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.80,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Forcing him into things isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.51,Italics,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We're not a sports club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.10,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.56,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.31,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,It's a club where we train in \Norder to feel telepathic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.48,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds shady as hell. \NWhat do you mean "telepathy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.03,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.28,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kageyama-kun has ESP,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.37,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,but aren't you using that \Nto get more customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.33,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a phony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.95,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth, amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.87,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare try to steal away my \Nstudent's precious time with your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.54,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.09,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you don't care \Nif our club gets abolished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.55,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be kicked out of the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.26,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Master, Senpai is about to cry, so I'm \Nthinking about joining after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.64,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.01,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Those are crocodile tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.35,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Bonds, memories, and friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Like any of those things will disappear \Nbecause a club is abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:16.73,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No! They just don't want to lose\Ntheir room, their budget
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:21.53,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,and their pointless after-school time, \Njudging from what their club sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.87,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,See through it, Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:27.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That shady club is going down \Nbecause it's meant to go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.96,Italics,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, hurry up and come to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.54,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.71,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I'll be leaving after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.92,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hear me out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.26,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the president \Nseriously believes in telepathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.81,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,but honestly, yeah, I just want to goof off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.52,Main,Nu,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, we're in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.48,Main,Nu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time we're going \Nto be able to goof off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.94,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Play cards with us in this lazy \Nlittle paradise we've created!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.65,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to find a more \Ncarefree club than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.82,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,We have until tomorrow, so think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.75,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,You're our last hope, Kageyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.67,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You properly declined, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.34,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No. I thought I'd think about it overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.59,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't procrastinate, Mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.59,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You need to properly decline things \Nthat you don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.22,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the thing I least want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.72,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,is be dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.68,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Highso Girls' Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.85,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's a private all-girls high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:37.15,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting the clients up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.77,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.69,sign_16058_256_Highso_Private_G,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Highso Private Girls' Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.69,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.03,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You! I'm talking to you! Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.32,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.45,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting from the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.08,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A suspicious individual showed up! \NRequesting backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.25,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a bit mean, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.62,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You perverted weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.17,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.42,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But thank goodness that they saw \Nthrough our disguises so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.00,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to infiltrate the school\Ndressed up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.34,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. Now hurry up \Nand get away from the pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.18,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.85,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deal with the suspicious individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:11.93,sign_16877_271_GO,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,G
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.73,sign_16877_271_GO,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.56,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
