Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:15.31,sign_13400_163_22__Until_Mob_Ex,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Progress toward Mob's Explosion: {\c&H86FF08&}34%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.98,sign_13400_163_22__Until_Mob_Ex,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Progress toward Mob's Explosion: {\c&H86FF08&}35%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:19.98,Show_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE2F88E&}Mob Psycho 100
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.74,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Won't I get in a lot of trouble\N if I'm busted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.75,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He said we were meeting on the roof, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.88,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.88,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from the consultation office.\NAre you the clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.01,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.35,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,An unfamiliar face. \NYou a transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:49.97,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.14,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Consultation office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.10,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to get through to us thugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.02,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:59.36,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like we're going to let some \Ntwerp like you lecture us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.15,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.03,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you mind your own business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.40,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you're going to regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.91,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.57,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about a downer. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.49,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.66,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.08,Main,Chiro,0000,0000,0000,,You promptly got picked on\N by thugs. How funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.09,sign_18511_301_Chihiro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.09,sign_18511_302_Clients,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Clients:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.09,sign_18511_303_Mari,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mari
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.54,sign_18524_302_We_re__your_clie,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,We're your clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.22,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Reigen guy coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.38,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He was caught at the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.55,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you both came here\Ndressed as girls? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.60,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't get us permission to come in,\Nso we didn't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.43,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.85,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you go through all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:43.23,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,The school just refuses \Nto take us seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.61,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.74,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Students' belongings have been disappearing\Nunder mysterious circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.49,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,and we've been hearing weird noises...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.24,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call it,\N a poltergeist phenomenon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.74,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,We heard things have been spotted \Nfloating through the air, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:59.54,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Apparently a bra started floating \Naround on its own in the locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.08,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Bra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:05.25,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead sure it has to be \Nsomething supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.34,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,So we just called the cheapest\Nexorcist in the area
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.30,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,and somehow ended up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:12.97,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:17.31,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,You're a guy, but you were trembling so much\Ndealing with some high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.98,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite the reliable gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.15,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.44,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,That was sarcasm, duh! \NShe wasn't complimenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.36,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we can trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.48,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,I have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.99,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,You seem unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.11,Main,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.24,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.24,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.74,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to perform an exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.46,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel anything spiritual, let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.42,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.76,Main,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you sense anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.63,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Just slightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.59,Italics,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's being serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.72,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It's here. Nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.47,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.35,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.77,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.69,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Something was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.07,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Something was looking in \Nfrom the top of the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.24,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,The windows are locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.95,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,And no one's gone through the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.57,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to follow the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.21,Main,Ari,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.92,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,We can trust you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.04,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.25,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.42,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.30,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:35.14,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep pursuing it, \Nit might try to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.97,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.31,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,The basketball team is practicing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.39,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.15,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I've trapped the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.07,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Pass! Pass! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.83,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.08,Main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.75,Main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.00,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.51,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Psychic brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:15.30,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trap me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.76,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to try to ruin my paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.31,sign_22787_368_Evil_Spirit__Sce,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(319,1)}Evil Spirit: Scent-Ghoul
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.31,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.28,Italics,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. I underestimated the psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.62,Italics,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't take a hostage, he'll erase me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.29,Italics,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,You smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.00,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,I choose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.00,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.50,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.32,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.48,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.32,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Want to go home together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.98,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.65,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What class is she in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.32,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.32,Main,Gil,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.20,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to them cheer. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.82,Main,Chihi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Apparently you were \Npretty reliable after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.37,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.71,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I was defeated \Nby a loser like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:30.38,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I'd finally \Nbe able to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:34.09,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be similar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.13,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:39.05,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,The way you get nervous around girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.64,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing the loser role in \Nyouth just like me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.64,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.98,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Things finally started to get \Nfun for me after I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.31,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,I was content.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.19,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.91,Main,Scent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are you living \Nevery day to the fullest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.21,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.71,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,You seem out of it. \NIs something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.26,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.30,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.60,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.43,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.89,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We believed in you, Kageyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.94,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry up and sign \Nthis club admission form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.15,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,You're already here? \NThat was awfully quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.65,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Vice President!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.37,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had to show this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.03,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,This room will become the club room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.46,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,for the newly formed Body Improvement Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.33,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.67,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,The Telepathy Club won't be abolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.55,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun here is just about to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.59,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.51,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.59,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.51,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,What grade are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.39,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.60,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any experience in other clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.60,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.23,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a close friend \Nin the Telepathy Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.77,Main,mob,0000,0000,0000,,I have an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.69,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you go to cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.48,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.40,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you study?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.40,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.36,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.03,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.40,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything\Nthat you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.61,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:26.12,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,If you let them goad you into joining\Ndespite having no interest in the club at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.99,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,what exactly will you gain from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.75,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just want to live \Nevery day to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.79,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,And will spending your time after school \Nwith cola, snacks and video games
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.00,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,help you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:40.63,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to join of your own free will,\N I will not stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.68,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,However, you should carefully \Nreconsider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.26,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you really want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.31,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.10,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have anything I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.39,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Does everyone else have something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.73,Italics,Ob,0000,0000,0000,,Something enjoyable?\NSomething I'm envious of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.69,Italics,Ob,0000,0000,0000,,What are they enjoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:02.70,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Clubs, hobbies, and studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:06.20,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging out with girls might be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.54,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I did have a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.45,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to confess my feelings to \Nmy first love, Tsubomi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.21,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,and walk home together, holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.29,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Tsubomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.84,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,When you make frogs float, \Nthey start swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.47,Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.43,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can make the bar all squishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.89,Flashback,Tsub,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Mob-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.64,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I'm only showing you, Tsubomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.23,Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.65,Flashback,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,The red team is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.20,Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,You're so fast, Akira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:50.74,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If I can change anything\Nby joining a club...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.66,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.50,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.67,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Body Improvement Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.00,Main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.26,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.76,Main,Prez,0000,0000,0000,,Good to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:07.68,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
